<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<Patch>

  <Operation Class="PatchOperationFindMod">
    <mods>
      <li>Rimsenal - Enhanced Vanilla Pack</li>
    </mods>
    <match Class="PatchOperationSequence">
      <success>Always</success>
      <operations>
	    <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName = "Apparel_TacVest"]/label</xpath>
            <value>
		      <label>전술 방탄복</label>
	        </value>
		</li>
		<li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName = "Apparel_TacVest"]/description</xpath>
            <value>
		      <description>인체 공학적으로 설계된 전술 방탄복입니다. 착용자의 전투 효율성을 향상시킵니다.</description>
	        </value>
		</li>
	  </operations>
    </match>
  </Operation>

  <Operation Class="PatchOperationFindMod">
    <mods>
      <li>Combat Extended</li>
    </mods>
    <match Class="PatchOperationSequence">
      <success>Always</success>
      <operations>
	    <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName = "Apparel_TacVest"]/label</xpath>
            <value>
		      <label>전술 조끼</label>
	        </value>
		</li>
		<li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName = "Apparel_TacVest"]/description</xpath>
            <value>
		      <description>탄창 및 기타 장비를 보관할 수 있는 많은 파우치가 달린 장비.\n\n재장전 속도를 높여주고 허용부피가 증가합니다.</description>
	        </value>
		</li>
	  </operations>
    </match>
  </Operation>

</Patch>